<P>
PARIS -- France has contacted Iraq on the dispute between
Baghdad and the United Nations special commission (UNSCOM) in
charge of disarmament in Iraq over the inspectors' access to the
presidential sites.
</P>
<P>
French Foreign Ministry spokeswoman Anne Gazeau-Secret said
France made the move to help solve the dispute.
(France-Iraq-Contact) 
</P>
