well as bonds of religion and culture, he added.
</P>
<P>
Osama, who is leading a delegation at a meeting of the
Pakistani-Saudi Joint Ministerial Commission, said that Saudi
Arabia and Pakistan should further strengthen bilateral trade and
economic cooperation.
</P>
<P>
He also said that the Pakistani-Saudi Investment Company should
be encouraged to play a more positive role in promoting economic
relations between the two countries. 
