<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, December 24 (Xinhua) -- Bangladesh and Japan signed an
agreement here Wednesday under which Japan will grant Bangladesh
9.659 billion yen (about 75 million U.S. dollars), the national
news agency BSS reported.
