mentioned grant for the effect of canceling an international debt
of Bangladesh.
</P>
<P>
The grant will enable Bangladesh to purchase commodities and
equipment from all member countries of the Organization for
Economic Cooperation and Development.
</P>
<P>
Since this grant is to be utilized by the Bangladeshi
government for importing commodities and equipment for investment
programs, it will contribute to the development of various sectors
of the Bangladeshi economy and social welfare, BSS said.
</P>
<P>
The grant will also contribute to improving the balance of
payments position of Bangladesh. 
