<HEADLINE> Shanghai Natural History Museum Has Precious Collection Insured </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, December 24 (Xinhua) -- The Shanghai Museum of
Natural History today bought an insurance policy worth more
than 20 million yuan (2.4 million US dollars) for the most
precious pieces among its collection.
</P>
<P>
The museum is the first to have its collection insured among
local museums. The insurer is Dazhong Insurance Company, a joint
stock company set up three years ago.
</P>
<P>
