public responsibility today.
</P>
<P>
Established in 1956, the Shanghai Museum of Natural History is
one of the largest of its kind in China. It has collected 240,000
pieces of samples, in which 184 are of high academic value, and
more than 9,000 books and periodicals.
</P>
<P>
