<HEADLINE> Australian Stocks Close Marginally Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, December 24 (Xinhua) -- The Australian sharemarket
finished Christmas Eve trading marginally down after a fall on
Wall Street overnight and ahead of a four-day national holiday.
</P>
<P>
