on dialogue among ancient civilizations, Kharrazi said the Greek
officials have expressed welcome to the idea.
</P>
<P>
Dialogue among ancient civilizations like Iran, Greece, Italy
and Egypt will promote understanding between nations, he said,
adding that Greek officials have voiced readiness to hold the
first round of such dialogue in Athens.
</P>
