During his stay in Athens, Kharrazi attended
Iran-Armenia-Greece trilateral meeting, and held separate talks
with Greek President Constantine Stephanopoulos, Prime Minister
Costas Simitis and Speaker of Parliament Apostolos Kaklamanis on
various issues. 
