former Prime Minister Shimon Peres, opposition Labor Party leader
Ehud Barak, and Leah Rabin, the widow of late Prime Minister
Yitzhak Rabin.
</P>
<P>
He paid a one-day visit to the Palestinian self-rule areas and
held talks with Palestinian President Yasser Arafat and Minister
of Planning and International Cooperation of the Palestinian
National Authority Nabil Sha'ath, in Gaza on December 23.
</P>
<P>
He reiterated China's support to the Palestinian just cause of
restoring their national rights, including the right to an
independent state.
</P>
<P>
Qian arrived in Tel Aviv December 21 after ending visits to
Lebanon and Syria in his multi-nation Middle East tour. 
