<HEADLINE> O'Neal to Miss Another Two Weeks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 23 (Xinhua) -- Los Angeles Lakers center
Shaquille O'Neal will miss at least two more weeks due to a
hairline fracture in his right wrist, according to a published
report on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
O'Neal, who has already missed five weeks with a strained
abdominal muscle, suffered his latest injury about two weeks ago
when he was punching a heavy bag, the Los Angeles Times reported.
</P>
