<HEADLINE> Cohen Leaves for Italy, Macedonia, Bosnia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 23 (Xinhua) -- U.S. Secretary of Defense
William Cohen left here today to visit U.S. forces in Italy,
Macedonia and Bosnia.
</P>
<P>
